# `prefect-gcp`

`prefect-gcp` makes it easy to leverage the capabilities of Google Cloud Platform (GCP) in your flows, featuring support for Vertex AI, Cloud Run, BigQuery, Cloud Storage, and Secret Manager. Visit the full docs [here](https://PrefectHQ.github.io/prefect-gcp). ### Installation To start using `prefect-gcp`: ```bash pip install prefect-gcp ``` To install extras, see [here](https://prefecthq.github.io/prefect-gcp/#installation). ### Contributing Thanks for thinking about chipping in! Check out this [step-by-step guide](https://prefecthq.github.io/prefect-gcp/#installation) on how to get started.
